    "dir": "this-sea-is-mine",
    "title": "This Sea Is Mine 🌊",
    "body": "A project born from a simple question: what does it mean to be separated from a sea that should already be yours?\n\nThrough landscapes, absence, and memory, this work reflects on borders, belonging, and the right to look toward one's own coast.\n\nGrateful to share this exhibition as the final project of my Master in Photography and Design at ELISAVA.\n\nThank you to everyone who joined me and supported this journey.",
